            <li>You have time for an 18–24 month process.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ch-decide-card">
          <div class="ch-decide-label">Choose Competent Authority if —</div>
          <ul>
            <li>You have UK, Ireland, USA, Canada or NZ experience.</li>
            <li>You want the fastest route to registration.</li>
            <li>You have the required supervised practice experience.</li>
            <li>You want to avoid AMC examinations entirely.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="ch-decide-card">
          <div class="ch-decide-label">Choose Specialist Pathway if —</div>
