      <!-- ===== PART III — WHEN TO START ===== -->
      <section class="ch-part">
        <div class="ch-part-num">Part Three</div>
        <h2 class="ch-h2">When to start.</h2>
        <p class="ch-deck-2">Optimal timing strategies and the financial planning that goes with them.</p>
      </section>

      <h3 class="ch-h3">During internship (recommended)</h3>
      <ul class="ch-bullets">
        <li>Start EPIC verification in months 6–8 of internship.</li>
        <li>Take AMC MCQ during the final months of internship.</li>
        <li><strong>Advantages:</strong> study momentum, financial support from family, time overlap.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="ch-h3">Post-internship</h3>
      <ul class="ch-bullets">
        <li>Requires 6–8 months dedicated preparation.</li>
        <li>Needs financial planning for the gap period.</li>
        <li><strong>Advantage:</strong> full focus on exam preparation without concurrent duties.</li>
      </ul>

